targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  $__time(timestamp/1000),
  engineeringvalue as "Active Power DG1"
FROM
  analogsignalfilteredlast
WHERE
 id=380 and
 timestamp >= $__unixEpochFrom()::bigint*1000 and
 timestamp <= $__unixEpochTo()::bigint*1000
order by timestamp;
